# Goose Hints for debbie.codes

## Verification Workflow
- Always use Playwright MCP to verify any work done on this repository
- Take a screenshot of the relevant page/changes after completing work
- Upload the screenshot to the PR to ensure easier verification for reviewers

## Content Guidelines
- Podcasts are stored in `content/podcasts/` directory
- Use only existing tags found in other content files
- Always include: title, date, description, url, image, tags, and host for podcasts
- Upload images to Cloudinary under `debbie.codes/` folder structure
